{"word":"G2301 - θεατρίζω - theatrízō - theh-at-rid'-zo - Make a gazing stock","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεατρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">theatrízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">theh-at-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make a gazing stock</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேடிக்கையாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to bring upon the stage"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2302 - θέατρον - théatron - theh'-at-ron/2302\">G2302</a>; to <i>expose as a spectacle:</i> - make a gazing stock.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2301/2301\">G2301</a>, <a href=\"#/G2302/2302\">G2302</a>"}]}